The right tool for our predicament.

00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:22.080
Your knee.

00:14:22.080 --> 00:14:23.080
It's okay, right?

00:14:24.580 --> 00:14:25.080
Sorry.

00:14:25.580 --> 00:14:27.580
The second half's only just started.

00:14:28.580 --> 00:14:31.580
How am I totally drained this early in the game?

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:33.080
Stupid question.

00:14:34.080 --> 00:14:37.080
That's the price for turning my back on the sport I love,

00:14:37.580 --> 00:14:39.080
looking for a reason to quit.

00:14:40.580 --> 00:14:44.080
Of course my body gives out at a crucial moment like this.

00:14:44.580 --> 00:14:45.580
I'm pathetic.

00:14:47.580 --> 00:14:48.580
Idiot.

00:14:48.580 --> 00:14:50.080
All that time wasted.

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:51.580
You could have trained,

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:53.580
but you were running away instead.

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:56.080
Jiggity.

00:14:56.580 --> 00:14:58.080
You were amazing.

00:15:00.580 --> 00:15:01.580
Damn it.

00:15:02.580 --> 00:15:04.080
Well, that's annoying.

00:15:04.580 --> 00:15:06.580
Things were just getting interesting.

00:15:07.580 --> 00:15:09.580
Oh, and Blue Lock calls time.

00:15:09.580 --> 00:15:11.080
They're sending in subs.

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:12.580
Looks like it's two at once.

00:15:12.580 --> 00:15:13.580
Mm-hmm.

00:15:13.580 --> 00:15:15.080
Number four, Hiyoma Jiggity,

00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:17.580
and number three, Ikiniko, are out.

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:20.080
Number 14, Bae Omikage,

00:15:20.080 --> 00:15:23.080
and number 16, Yohiro Riyo, are substituted in.

00:15:29.080 --> 00:15:30.080
Great job, man.

00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:32.080
It's up to you now.

00:15:33.580 --> 00:15:35.080
It was a good run, Jiggity.

00:15:35.580 --> 00:15:36.080
Rest up.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:38.080
I've got you covered.

00:15:41.080 --> 00:15:42.580
Nice sprinting, number four!

00:15:42.580 --> 00:15:43.580
Yeah!

00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:45.580
You were amazing out there!

00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:53.080
Hey, what's your deal?

00:15:55.080 --> 00:15:57.580
If you've got a problem with being substituted,

00:15:57.580 --> 00:15:59.080
better speak up.

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.080
No.

00:16:02.580 --> 00:16:03.580
I don't, sir!

00:16:07.080 --> 00:16:08.580
If you want to stay in,

00:16:08.580 --> 00:16:11.580
take to the field with a body that can last a whole match,

00:16:11.580 --> 00:16:12.580
idiot.

00:16:14.580 --> 00:16:16.580
Listen to that frustration.

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:20.080
It's telling you how far you still have to go.

00:16:23.080 --> 00:16:25.080
And after swapping out those two players,

00:16:25.080 --> 00:16:27.580
seems Blue Lock's also changing up some positions.

00:16:27.580 --> 00:16:28.580
Yep, it sure does.

00:16:28.580 --> 00:16:30.580
Meanwhile, the U-20s are in control.

00:16:30.580 --> 00:16:32.580
The momentum is on their side.

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:35.080
Let's see how things look after those changes.

00:16:35.080 --> 00:16:37.080
Ten minutes into the second half.

00:16:37.080 --> 00:16:38.580
Should be interesting.

00:16:40.080 --> 00:16:41.580
You're a fullback, Otoya.

00:16:41.580 --> 00:16:43.080
Don't venture too far forward.

00:16:43.580 --> 00:16:44.580
Yeah, yeah.

00:16:46.080 --> 00:16:47.580
I'm finally back.

00:16:48.580 --> 00:16:50.080
On the pitch with him again.

00:16:52.580 --> 00:16:53.580
Nagi.

00:16:55.580 --> 00:16:56.580
Wait long?

00:17:04.579 --> 00:17:05.579
Nah.

00:17:05.579 --> 00:17:07.079
I was certain you'd be here.

00:17:10.079 --> 00:17:11.579
Score another goal already.

00:17:11.579 --> 00:17:14.079
You're capable of more than one.

00:17:14.079 --> 00:17:16.079
Yeah, I know.

00:17:17.079 --> 00:17:19.079
If we don't win, then it's over.

00:17:19.579 --> 00:17:21.079
It's too soon.

00:17:21.079 --> 00:17:23.079
We can't let our dreams die here.

00:17:24.079 --> 00:17:26.079
Yeah, I'm aware.

00:17:28.579 --> 00:17:30.079
We're still tied.

00:17:30.579 --> 00:17:34.079
The next goal will determine who's in control of the game.

00:17:34.579 --> 00:17:35.579
This hit.

00:17:38.079 --> 00:17:40.079
The turning point of the battle.

00:17:41.579 --> 00:17:42.579
The final goal.

00:17:42.579 --> 00:17:45.579
With Hiyori added to the front line, our tactics have changed.

00:17:46.579 --> 00:17:48.579
Let's show them our attacking options.

00:17:48.579 --> 00:17:50.579
What we practiced in Blue Lock.

00:17:51.579 --> 00:17:54.579
Until now, we've had everyone running around the field.

00:17:54.579 --> 00:17:59.579
With Rin as our core, each player used their individual skills without pausing.

00:18:00.579 --> 00:18:04.579
But Hiyori's strengths are his unhurried vision and his controlled touch.

00:18:05.579 --> 00:18:09.079
He's a calm tactician who creates space on the front line.

00:18:09.079 --> 00:18:11.079
I'm not letting you pass me, little boy Blue.

00:18:11.579 --> 00:18:15.579
Well, my tattooed friend, that's fine.

00:18:15.579 --> 00:18:18.579
See, I'm neither a ninja nor a sprinter.

00:18:18.579 --> 00:18:20.579
I compete in a different way.

00:18:23.579 --> 00:18:27.579
Hiyori wasn't subbed in for one-on-ones that glide past an opponent.

00:18:27.579 --> 00:18:32.579
But for his inspirational passes and how they coordinate with our movements.

00:18:32.579 --> 00:18:34.579
Aggression isn't the only ego.

00:18:36.579 --> 00:18:38.579
I have my own kind.

00:18:38.579 --> 00:18:40.579
I'm a true warrior.

00:18:40.579 --> 00:18:42.579
So fast, outside of the boot?

00:18:42.579 --> 00:18:43.579
That's tight!

00:18:43.579 --> 00:18:47.579
Forcing it through a tiny gap, huh? That's kinda hot.

00:18:47.579 --> 00:18:49.579
As always, you're only good at kicking!

00:18:49.579 --> 00:18:51.579
Don't you say only.

00:18:51.579 --> 00:18:54.579
Then prove it already that you ain't mediocre.

00:18:55.579 --> 00:18:58.579
Ka-ka-ka, what a noisy crow.

00:18:59.579 --> 00:19:02.579
Their passing back and forth caught the other team off guard.

00:19:03.579 --> 00:19:07.579
Now that they've earned some space, I need to react reflexively to Hiyori's cool-headedness.

00:19:07.579 --> 00:19:09.579
And that left foot!

00:19:10.579 --> 00:19:12.579
Alright, here goes.

00:19:18.579 --> 00:19:21.579
Her trajectory is as nasty as Saito's.

00:19:21.579 --> 00:19:23.579
Where's the target? Is it green?

00:19:23.579 --> 00:19:24.579
No, beyond him!

00:19:25.579 --> 00:19:27.579
Sick pass. Thank you.

00:19:27.579 --> 00:19:29.579
THINK AGAIN!

00:19:29.579 --> 00:19:31.579
Don't you dare think of him until you make it past me!

00:19:31.579 --> 00:19:33.579
Go ahead and kick it, beauty trapper!

00:19:35.579 --> 00:19:36.579
This Doberman is so annoying.

00:19:37.579 --> 00:19:40.579
I managed to sneak in behind using Rin as bait.

00:19:40.579 --> 00:19:42.579
Oh, and here comes the ball.

00:19:43.579 --> 00:19:44.579
Aw man.

00:19:44.579 --> 00:19:46.579
What do I do? Guess I'll jump!

00:19:47.579 --> 00:19:50.579
And find an open space? It's my only option!

00:19:50.579 --> 00:19:53.579
I know you can sense it. It's yours!

00:19:54.579 --> 00:19:55.579
Striker!

00:19:56.579 --> 00:19:59.579
Here it comes! Finally, a pass behind Rin!

00:20:00.579 --> 00:20:01.579
I won't hesitate!

00:20:03.579 --> 00:20:05.579
Direct shot!

00:20:05.579 --> 00:20:06.579
Freeze, burglar.

00:20:07.579 --> 00:20:09.579
I'm not going to let you get away with this.

00:20:09.579 --> 00:20:11.579
You thought I wasn't going to put a collar on you?

00:20:13.579 --> 00:20:15.579
Aiku! Where did he come from?

00:20:17.579 --> 00:20:21.579
We only just changed up our attack, and that was Nagi's improvised pass!

00:20:23.579 --> 00:20:26.579
I reacted first, but he still got here before I did!

00:20:27.579 --> 00:20:30.579
As long as I'm in his territory, my abilities are dead!

00:20:31.579 --> 00:20:32.579
Damn you!

00:20:33.579 --> 00:20:34.579
Watch for the counter!

00:20:34.579 --> 00:20:35.579
Yep, that's our captain.

00:20:35.579 --> 00:20:36.579
Counting on you!

00:20:37.579 --> 00:20:38.579
I'll count on you, genius!

00:20:39.579 --> 00:20:42.579
Incoming! He'll pass it to Shido!

00:20:42.579 --> 00:20:44.579
We'll stop him here.

00:20:44.579 --> 00:20:46.579
You ready, Reio?

00:20:47.579 --> 00:20:50.579
Listen up, Reio Mikage.

00:20:50.579 --> 00:20:53.579
There's only one reason I'm swapping you in.

00:20:53.579 --> 00:20:56.579
I want you to focus on stopping Shido.

00:20:57.579 --> 00:21:00.579
Right. I worked on my defending back at the training camp.

00:21:01.579 --> 00:21:03.579
And have been keeping an eye on the game like you said.

00:21:03.579 --> 00:21:06.579
Specifically, the abilities of the other team's defenders.

00:21:07.579 --> 00:21:09.579
I'm sure you'll be able to see them.

00:21:09.579 --> 00:21:11.579
Shido and Sai Itoshi.

00:21:12.579 --> 00:21:14.579
I'll keep them in my sight at all times.

00:21:15.579 --> 00:21:17.579
He's still dribbling.

00:21:18.579 --> 00:21:19.579
Has it made a move?

00:21:20.579 --> 00:21:21.579
Not yet.

00:21:23.579 --> 00:21:24.579
The combo!

00:21:24.579 --> 00:21:25.579
Right!

00:21:37.579 --> 00:21:38.579
I'll take it.

00:21:38.579 --> 00:21:39.579
Huh?

00:21:39.579 --> 00:21:44.579
That move… It's mine!

00:21:45.579 --> 00:21:48.579
Replication was 99% successful.

00:21:50.579 --> 00:21:51.579
This is my role!

00:21:51.579 --> 00:21:53.579
The entire reason I'm in this game!

00:21:55.579 --> 00:21:57.579
Chameleon Defense!

00:21:58.579 --> 00:21:59.579
Reio…

00:21:59.579 --> 00:22:01.579
Props, man.

00:22:02.579 --> 00:22:04.579
With this power of mine…

00:22:04.579 --> 00:22:06.579
I'll put an end to Shido!

00:22:15.579 --> 00:22:19.579
I wake up in the morning

00:22:19.579 --> 00:22:22.579
And the sound of the bell rings

00:22:23.579 --> 00:22:26.579
The blues of the night

00:22:27.579 --> 00:22:33.579
I see a dream that's so lonely and fleeting

00:22:33.579 --> 00:22:37.579
I dream of a dream

00:22:37.579 --> 00:22:39.579
The seasons pass by

00:22:39.579 --> 00:22:40.579
Still I'm standing

00:22:40.579 --> 00:22:42.579
I'm still here

00:22:42.579 --> 00:22:43.579
With memories,

00:22:43.579 --> 00:22:44.579
I'm growing and growing

00:22:44.579 --> 00:22:45.579
Scars

00:22:45.579 --> 00:22:48.579
I can touch them again and again

00:22:48.579 --> 00:22:51.579
This flame is dyed blue

00:22:51.579 --> 00:22:53.579
Quietly, hotly

00:22:53.579 --> 00:22:56.579
I reflect on my chest

00:22:56.579 --> 00:23:00.579
I don't feel like I'll ever disappear

00:23:00.579 --> 00:23:02.579
Overflowing,

00:23:02.579 --> 00:23:05.579
I'm still in love

00:23:05.579 --> 00:23:10.579
I'm in love

00:23:10.579 --> 00:23:12.579
With only one thing

00:23:12.579 --> 00:23:15.579
One dream

00:23:15.579 --> 00:23:17.579
That's all I have

00:23:17.579 --> 00:23:18.579
One day

00:23:18.579 --> 00:23:21.579
I'm just staring at one place

00:23:21.579 --> 00:23:23.579
I can't go back to those days

00:23:23.579 --> 00:23:25.579
Now, it's too late

00:23:25.579 --> 00:23:27.579
Oh yeah, yeah, yeah

00:23:27.579 --> 00:23:30.579
Oh yeah, yeah, yeah

00:23:30.579 --> 00:23:31.579
Just one day

00:23:32.579 --> 00:23:34.579
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

00:23:34.579 --> 00:23:38.579
Before long, yeah

00:23:40.579 --> 00:23:41.579
Blue lock!

00:23:41.579 --> 00:23:43.579
Additional time!

00:23:44.579 --> 00:23:47.579
So, is watching soccer games something you guys do often?

00:23:47.579 --> 00:23:48.579
Who, us?

00:23:48.579 --> 00:23:50.579
No, no, Yoichi does, of course.

00:23:50.579 --> 00:23:53.579
But I'm sorry to say we don't know anything about the sport.

00:23:53.579 --> 00:23:54.579
I'm the same.

00:23:54.579 --> 00:23:56.579
Like with off-sides, or whatnot.

00:23:56.579 --> 00:23:58.579
I'm still so confused by it.

00:23:58.579 --> 00:23:59.579
Me as well!

00:23:59.579 --> 00:24:01.579
The whole thing's this big mystery I'll never get.

00:24:01.579 --> 00:24:02.579
Right?

00:24:02.579 --> 00:24:04.579
I'm glad I'm right there with you.

00:24:04.579 --> 00:24:05.579
I meant it before.

00:24:05.579 --> 00:24:07.579
I'm grateful our sons have become good friends.

00:24:07.579 --> 00:24:10.579
You see, my Meguru, he doesn't exactly have tons.

00:24:10.579 --> 00:24:12.579
The pleasure is all ours.

00:24:12.579 --> 00:24:14.579
Actually, Yoichi's kind of in the same boat.

00:24:14.579 --> 00:24:15.579
Oh?

00:24:15.579 --> 00:24:17.579
Can you tell me a little more about him?

00:24:17.579 --> 00:24:21.579
I guess, if I'm being honest, he's a scaredy-cat.

00:24:21.579 --> 00:24:23.579
Wow, is he really?

00:24:23.579 --> 00:24:25.579
One time, when he was playing in the park,

00:24:25.579 --> 00:24:27.579
he put his hands on his head and started crying.

00:24:27.579 --> 00:24:30.579
He thought a storm cloud was about to form and start raining on him.

00:24:30.579 --> 00:24:31.579
So yeah, that's pretty much it.

00:24:31.579 --> 00:24:34.579
That's pretty much my sensitive chicken little for you.

00:24:34.579 --> 00:24:35.579
Aww.

00:24:35.579 --> 00:24:38.579
I love that he senses things before they happen.

00:24:38.579 --> 00:24:40.579
Sounds like he's a genius.

00:24:40.579 --> 00:24:42.579
Mine's the complete opposite.

00:24:42.579 --> 00:24:45.579
He'll see kids drawing a red or yellow sun and say,

00:24:45.579 --> 00:24:46.579
That's just weird.

00:24:46.579 --> 00:24:47.579
The sun is white.

00:24:47.579 --> 00:24:48.579
See?

00:24:48.579 --> 00:24:49.579
Are you even looking?

00:24:49.579 --> 00:24:51.579
And then start a fight over it.

00:24:51.579 --> 00:24:52.579
Also, he gets naked all the time.

00:24:52.579 --> 00:24:53.579
What?

00:24:53.579 --> 00:24:54.579
Yoichi's the same way.

00:24:54.579 --> 00:24:55.579
A little nudist.

00:24:55.579 --> 00:24:58.579
He's always taking off his clothes and complaining.

00:24:58.579 --> 00:25:00.579
Apparently, he hates how they feel and says they chafe.

00:25:00.579 --> 00:25:04.579
It sounds like soccer isn't our son's only shared interest.

00:25:04.579 --> 00:25:05.579
Guess not.

00:25:06.579 --> 00:25:08.579
But I'm glad that he found this sport.

00:25:08.579 --> 00:25:10.579
Because of it, he's able to make friends.

00:25:10.579 --> 00:25:12.579
And he was lucky enough to meet your boy.

00:25:12.579 --> 00:25:13.579
Yes.

00:25:13.579 --> 00:25:16.579
And I look forward to a long-lasting friendship of our own.

00:25:16.579 --> 00:25:18.579
Hey, there you are.

00:25:18.579 --> 00:25:20.579
The second half is about to start, you two.

00:25:20.579 --> 00:25:21.579
We should get your...

00:25:21.579 --> 00:25:22.579
Whoa!

00:25:22.579 --> 00:25:24.579
Oh!

00:25:24.579 --> 00:25:25.579
Oh!

00:25:25.579 --> 00:25:26.579
Oh!

00:25:26.579 --> 00:25:28.579
Help me!

00:25:28.579 --> 00:25:29.579
Oh!

00:25:30.579 --> 00:25:31.579
Whoa!

00:25:31.579 --> 00:25:32.579
Nice combination play!

00:25:32.579 --> 00:25:33.579
Oh!

00:25:33.579 --> 00:25:34.579
Oh!

00:25:34.579 --> 00:25:35.579
Oh!

